{"tid":2308617,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚得志案件　控方申請交國安法指定法官處理","createTime":"2020-12-02T04:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T06:50:49.000Z","uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3f3587c3a39f44b2ecdc478e83b49e9a6b0ab1af","tid":2308617,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:30:17.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】人民力量譚得志被控發表煽動文字等14項控罪，區域法院處理控方申請，要求將案件交由國安法指定法官處理 。<br />\n<br />\n譚得志由囚車押到區域法院。控方指，國安法第44條強制要求危害國家安全的案件要由指定法官審理，若由非指定法官審理，其所作的裁決或決定屬越權，亦有機會被司法覆核；又指，指定法官本身可審理非涉及國家安全的案件，不認為對被告造成任何不公。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指，國安法下並非要設立一個新法庭，所有裁判官或法官的司法管轄權並無改變。若一名非指定法官亦有能力去處理涉及國安法的案件，其所作決定不會被司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n區域法院決定交由國安法指定法官，決定案件是否涉國安法，要由指定法官審理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=415052\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415052&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2ZhvY2R4XAiH6OvuWOSnKsk%3D&h=12ed1669\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415052&h=639b5340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=415052</a>"},{"pid":"f27ecc76b70226d73696752c9f284579e6c88719","tid":2308617,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:34:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5a130c99b4bc5a6346f5e85e0334dddb67ac3a","tid":2308617,"uid":331739,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:36:22.000Z","msg":"而家睇返人力先最有guts <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8c4c22e03a9cdd9fc1d23ae4e1008415c91f76","tid":2308617,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:38:06.000Z","msg":"到宜家都講唔出係唔係犯左國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55978fc9bff018199209e9f153c0e7d054